<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> O Sult&atilde;o Bonacheir&atilde;o</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Era um sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a>.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Sentado em almofadas, bem instalado, de pernas cruzadas, o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a> ouvia, sorria e calava.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Vinham ministros falar-lhe das arcas dos tesouros do reino quase vazias, e o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a> ouvia, sorria e calava.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Vinham generais falar-lhe da <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[9],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">imin&ecirc;ncia</a> de guerras desastrosas, de inimigos do reino que rondavam as fronteiras, e o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a> ouvia, sorria e calava.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Vinham mensageiros falar-lhe de desastres sem fim: secas nas prov&iacute;ncias ocidentais, avalanches nas prov&iacute;ncias orientais, bandos de salteadores desenfreados nas prov&iacute;ncias da montanha, inunda&ccedil;&otilde;es, naufr&aacute;gios, mis&eacute;ria na prov&iacute;ncia litoral, e o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a> ouvia, sorria e calava.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Tanto sorria e tanto calava que os ministros, os generais e os mensageiros desistiram de lhe falar.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Um por um, foram abandonando o pal&aacute;cio do sult&atilde;o, e com eles sa&iacute;ram os <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[10],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">cortes&atilde;os</a>, os guardas e os criados.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Ficou o sult&atilde;o sozinho, sentado em almofadas, de pernas cruzadas, sorrindo, sorrindo sempre.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mas a certa altura, o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a> sentiu uma comich&atilde;o na m&atilde;o. Eram duas formigas.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Dizia uma para a outra:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Estou desconfiada que somos as &uacute;ltimas.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- As aranhas j&aacute; fecharam com as suas teias as portas do pal&aacute;cio. As portas e as janelas - dizia a outra.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Despachemo-nos, despachemo-nos - diziam as duas, enquanto atravessavam a m&atilde;o do sult&atilde;o, desciam pelas almofadas e corriam pelo ch&atilde;o... </div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O sult&atilde;o deixou de sorrir.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Esperem por mim - balbuciou, levantando-se a custo.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Foi atr&aacute;s das formigas e enfiou por um subterr&acirc;neo do pal&aacute;cio, onde se <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[11],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">enfarruscou</a> todo, a ponto de, uma vez c&aacute; fora, ningu&eacute;m o reconhecer como sult&atilde;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Havia grande agita&ccedil;&atilde;o na pra&ccedil;a, diante do pal&aacute;cio.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- O pr&iacute;ncipe Aldi tomou sobre si o governo do reino. &Eacute; um pr&iacute;ncipe bom e corajoso. Vai dar um bom sult&atilde;o - informou um homem, passando pelo sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a>, que n&atilde;o sorria.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- O antigo sult&atilde;o era um paspalh&atilde;o. N&atilde;o prestava para nada, n&atilde;o sabia governar - disse outro homem, passando pelo sult&atilde;o, que n&atilde;o sorria.  - A estas horas ainda deve estar no pal&aacute;cio, de pernas cruzadas sobre uma montanha de almofadas. Sult&atilde;o paspalh&atilde;o! Vamos l&aacute; n&oacute;s e cai tudo ao ch&atilde;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Vamos! Vamos! - gritaram v&aacute;rias vozes. 
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Desta vez o sult&atilde;o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[8],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">bonacheir&atilde;o</a>, vendo-os ir em direc&ccedil;&atilde;o ao pal&aacute;cio, ouvi-os, sorriu e calou-se.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Escapou-se.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=10&Dia=05','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
